    "rationale": "The FEA modeling framework demonstrated adequate predictive capability for the non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending COU. All quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, QoI difference < 10%) were satisfied across all three quantities of interest. The overall evidence package is considered sufficient to support regulatory submission, notwithstanding that the Test conditions factor did not reach its required level and that several factors were evaluated without formal level assignments.",
